<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٣ - نا مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> وقَالَ الْحَسَنُ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُشْبِهُ بَعْضُهَا بَعْضًا , لَيْسَ فِيهَا مِنْ رَذْلٍ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>